Enum CODACommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<CODACommand>
      • org.jlab.coda.emu.support.codaComponent.CODACommand
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<CODACommand>

    public enum CODACommand
extends java.lang.Enum<CODACommand>
    This class enumerates all the commands that Run Control can send to this Emu. These objects only contain static data.

    timmer Date: 3/14/11
